claim.claim-text:
A binding according to claim 1, characterized in that for classic style skiing:
- said flange (31) and said base (24) of the cleat (30) are separate pieces, whereupon said base is inside said flange which surrounds the base respectively;
- said binding (1) further comprises a swivel (35), which has an axis line (36) across a separate base (24) and a separate flange (31) to be parallel with said width (W) of the ski (10), and first holes (33) for first fastening elements (34) in said separate base (24).
